{
  "stem": "15943.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't, you know, you have to write on this topic, do research, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Express your thoughts.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Pick a topic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember in Yiddish I wrote an essay called [YIDDISH], 'What the Doll Is Telling Me.' My mother had made a doll out of pieces of fabric.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We couldn't afford it, those big fancy dolls that they had in stores.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So she made a cloth doll out of fabric.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what the doll is telling me-- what did the doll tell me?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How hard my mother's working.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How much love she puts in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I guess it was a good essay because the teacher made me go around read it to the other students.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, everybody spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this became the beginning of my creativity because they-- everybody seemed to have-- seemed to like it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I felt that I could express something, and I started writing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How old were you when you first started to write like that?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "10 Years old.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My uncle was a teacher there, and-- my mother's brother-- and of course, he knew everything that was going on-- the good and the bad.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Funny thing about school too-- I was supposed to wear glasses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you know, girls at that age, glasses, it wasn't right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I didn't wear the glasses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I came to school, and I didn't tell the teacher that I don't see the blackboard.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I waited.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When class was finished, I would run over to the border and quickly write down what was on the board.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So she didn't know that I can't see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one day we had an inspector, and the inspectors from the Board of Education, they were very strict.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They wanted-- they were looking for excuses to close the Jewish schools.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
